			<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
				<p class="js-fade-in text-center text-base font-medium text-white/90 sm:text-lg">
					Revenue-focused marketing operators, not a fractional CMO service.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- SECTION 3 – PROBLEM (bg-slate-950) -->
		<section class="bg-slate-950 py-16 sm:py-20" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
				<div class="js-fade-in max-w-2xl">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-marketing">The marketing talent gap</p>
					<h2 id="problem-heading" class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-4xl">
						The Marketing Talent Gap Is Stalling Growth
					</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
						Experienced channel operators are scarce and expensive. Teams run understaffed while pipelines stall and campaigns slip.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-marketing">Stat</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">3.8%</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-100">unemployment in marketing roles</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
							Skilled operators are rare. Hiring cycles stretch for months.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-marketing">Stat</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">MarTech</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-100">skills gap in marketing ops</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
