		</section>

		<!-- SECTION 4 – SOLUTION OVERVIEW (bg-slate-900/40) -->
		<section class="bg-slate-900/40 py-16 sm:py-20" aria-labelledby="solution-heading">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
				<div class="js-fade-in max-w-2xl">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sky-300">What you get</p>
					<h2 id="solution-heading" class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-4xl">
						Full-Time Dedicated Specialists Embedded in Your Team
					</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
						Not fractional. Not agency project work. One specialist (or a pod) working exclusively for you – your channels, your goals, your stack.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-marketing">âœ“ Dedicated</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">40h/week or 20h/week – they're yours, not shared.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-marketing">âœ“ NOT fractional</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">No part-time CMO or advisory-only engagements.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-marketing">âœ“ NOT agency project work</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Embedded operators, not retainer-based project sprints.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="js-fade-in rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-marketing">âœ“ Month-to-month</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Scale up or down. Free replacement guarantee.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- SECTION 5 – OPS-FIRST WEDGE (bg-slate-950) -->
		<section class="bg-slate-950 py-16 sm:py-20" aria-labelledby="ops-heading">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
				<div class="js-fade-in max-w-2xl">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-marketing">Entry point</p>
					<h2 id="ops-heading" class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-4xl">
						MarOps / RevOps as Your Entry Point
					</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
						Many teams start with marketing operations or RevOps – HubSpot, Salesforce, Klaviyo certified operators who clean up infrastructure, reporting, and lifecycle. Then add channel specialists.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
